{"tid":1070096,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亞洲電視料年度虧損將大幅增加","createTime":"2019-03-20T11:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T13:35:21.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d9f509a4777ff84ce17e74da2b2491f470a17a95","tid":1070096,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T11:39:50.000Z","msg":"亞洲電視控股(<a href=\"http://00707.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00707.HK&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV3f7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=3c271395\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00707.HK</a>)  沽空 $9.18千; 比率 0.134%   發盈警，預期截至2018年12月31日止年度錄得之虧損將按年大幅增加，主要是由於收購亞洲電視有限公司及其附屬公司所產生的商譽減值虧損；聯營公司的權益減值虧損；確認無形資產的減值虧損；因收購亞視而涉及新發展的媒體，文化及娛樂業務導致營運開支增加等原因所致。(jc/a)(報價延遲最少十五分鐘。沽空資料截至 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.930172/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.930172%2F2&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV3f7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=99617334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.930172/2</a>"},{"pid":"9dea1bf8954d222fbcceaf8639a4c8631b713b61","tid":1070096,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T11:41:22.000Z","msg":"無線又蝕，亞視又蝕，一齊執柒左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0785bb2ea9f718818d149b9b82ff15ef04cbdb1","tid":1070096,"uid":38651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T11:42:45.000Z","msg":"原來亞視仲未執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2d6ca2ea59b1f78ce7bec77a42576fb513e815","tid":1070096,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T11:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads//2015/04/1610910_365481376993541_7059697918093039864_n-650x278.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.li